  accountAccessKey?: string(name='accountAccessKey', description='The AccessKey ID of your Alibaba Cloud account or RAM user. For more information about how to obtain an AccessKey ID, see [Create an AccessKey](https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/116401.html).

