- `dedicated`: The dedicated architecture, which is applicable to reserved and elastic (dedicated) instances.', example='shared'),
  encryptedInstance?: boolean(name='EncryptedInstance', description='This parameter is applicable only to dedicated instances. Specifies whether to enable data-at-rest encryption for the instance.', example='false'),
  instanceName?: string(name='InstanceName', description='The name of the instance. The name can be up to 64 characters long.', example='amqp-xxxxx'),
  instanceType?: string(name='InstanceType', description='The instance type.
